graph TD
    %% Déclencheurs de la pipeline
    A[Push/PR sur main] --> B{backend job}

    %% Subgraph CI (Continuous Integration)
    subgraph CI["🔄 Continuous Integration"]
        B --> C[Checkout repository]
        C --> D[Set up JDK 17]
        D --> E[Cache Gradle packages]
        E --> F[Run tests + coverage<br/>jacocoTestReport]
        F --> G{Tests réussis?}
        G -->|✅ Oui| H[Verify tests passed<br/>✅ Tests réussis]
        G -->|❌ Non| I[Tests failed - Block deployment<br/>❌ Échec + exit 1]
        H --> J[Build backend JAR<br/>-x test]
        J --> K[Upload coverage report]
        K --> L[Upload JAR artifact]
        L --> M[SonarCloud Scan<br/>Analyse qualité code]
    end

    %% Connexion CI vers CD avec condition
    M --> N{Conditions CD?}
    N -->|✅ backend.result == 'success'<br/>&& push sur main<br/>&& pas PR| O[deploy job]

    %% Subgraph CD (Continuous Deployment)
    subgraph CD["🚀 Continuous Deployment"]
        O --> P[Checkout repository]
        P --> Q[Download JAR artifact]
        Q --> R[Set up Docker Buildx]
        R --> S[Login to GHCR]
        S --> T[Extract metadata<br/>pour tagging]
        T --> U[Build & Push Docker image<br/>multi-platform<br/>linux/amd64,arm64]
        U --> V[✅ Image déployée<br/>sur GHCR]
    end

    %% Styles pour les nœuds d'échec
    classDef failure fill:#ff6b6b,stroke:#d63031,color:#fff
    classDef success fill:#51cf66,stroke:#40c057,color:#fff
    classDef condition fill:#ffd43b,stroke:#fab005,color:#000

    I:::failure
    H:::success
    N:::condition
    V:::success